## Modo com Attributes/EntityManager

```pascal
uses Providers.Attributers, Providers.Database.EntityManager;

[Table('clientes')]
TCliente = class
  [PrimaryKey] [Field('id')]    property Id: Integer read FId write FId;
  [Field('nome', 100)]          property Nome: string read FNome write FNome;
end;

// Uso:
LEM := TEntityManager.New.Connection(LConn);
LEM.Save(LCliente);                          // INSERT ou UPDATE (Id > 0)
LCliente := LEM.Find<TCliente>(42);          // SELECT por PK
LList    := LEM.FindAll<TCliente>;           // SELECT *
LEM.Delete<TCliente>(42);                    // DELETE por PK
```

