## Pool de conexĂµes

```pascal
LPool := TPoolConnections.New;
LPool.TryAdd(TConnection.New.FromConfig);    // adicionar ao pool

LConn := LPool.GetFromPool;                  // pegar (FIFO)
try
  // usar LConn normalmente
finally
  LPool.ReturnToPool(LConn);                 // devolver
end;
```

